# 15-feature-development-workflow.mdc

---
description: Feature implementation workflow
---

Before implementing features:

1. Identify affected domain.
2. Check existing patterns.
3. Define interfaces.
4. Consider security.
5. Add tests.
6. Update documentation.

Prefer:

Small incremental changes.

Avoid:

Large unrelated modifications.
